{"tid":543631,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"乜lalaland真係吹大咗？","createTime":"2018-01-28T16:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T14:43:42.000Z","uid":123034,"like":33,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"83c8a9f0ce28b215861b2356b0a3ca4968306d59","tid":543631,"uid":123034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:32:37.000Z","msg":"見好多連登仔都話垃圾又話吹大咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我又覺得套戲未至於去到吹大咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其中有三幕戲都好精采<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男主角第一次約女主角去酒吧，男主角同女主角爭論又話要守護傳承好爵士樂勁正，完全感受到男主角份堅持，唔放棄。可能我係香港人代入咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二幕就有啲行嘅，就係男女主角燭光晚餐，理想同現實嘅抉擇。<br />\n<br />\n但最後個幕真係神級，爵士樂同條女嘅矛盾位用8分鐘去完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:唔識睇戲但鍾意睇戲"},{"pid":"e6143877cdba95c2dea26ed1610ff3641ba59977","tid":543631,"uid":80503,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:35:33.000Z","msg":"結局真係無敵"},{"pid":"827e66bf69034a9a852f85bcf496b53dcfdc70fc","tid":543631,"uid":54785,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:41:07.000Z","msg":"認真製作 每一幕歌幕都有特別, 開場更加係正, 一shot 直落, 始終套戲係sell 感受同視覺效果, 劇情我覺得正常交代到又有驚喜, 仲想點, 唔通下下都要鐵達尼咁先係好戲咩"},{"pid":"c90bb4b39262ecbb28f16f82c58414ca4d3d1f60","tid":543631,"uid":5443,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"睇完勁心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a1c783d96f9b177d65fdb0ec6e89914113f964","tid":543631,"uid":4260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:05:07.000Z","msg":"我諗有人不滿既部份原因，係mia個角色本身有另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec93d740c8768fe8630daf2dd6d461b952d20c7","tid":543631,"uid":41969,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quot